That I attended a public event.

396
00:14:46,692 --> 00:14:48,426
Yo, Ron?
Come on, bud.

397
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:49,594
We're gonna go play some
video games

398
00:14:49,628 --> 00:14:52,263
