to call my friend.

434
00:16:28,727 --> 00:16:32,463
Pretty good speech.
I mean, it was, um...

435
00:16:32,498 --> 00:16:35,433
a little sappy, maybe.

436
00:16:36,435 --> 00:16:39,370
I think I liked it.

437
00:16:45,744 --> 00:16:47,578
Jessica, Mr. Nelson.

438
00:16:47,613 --> 00:16:49,747
